    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good summary. i've heard some people say that it's basically just a way for conservative judges to get the outcomes they want by pretending it's about the text. how would an originalist respond to the criticism that it's often used just for political reasons?",
      "source": "evaluator"
